<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>イトー市・タクボクエストⅱ ～欠如した説明責任とカオスの中で～</title>
    <!-- Chosen Palette: Retro RPG Blue -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A 5-chapter narrative SPA designed as a retro JRPG. This structure was chosen to make a complex political conflict engaging. The user journey begins with selecting a 'citizen' stance, which personalizes the experience by setting an initial 'Trust Gauge'. A new character introduction section deepens the narrative. The core of the application is Chapter 3, a 'Command Battle' UI, which directly addresses the user's request to emphasize the mayor-council conflict. This turn-based simulation visualizes their escalating actions and reactions, making the abstract political struggle tangible and exciting. The flow concludes with a choice-driven scenario exploration, solidifying the user's understanding of the stakes. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
- Character Profiles: Goal: Narrative Depth. Method: Styled HTML cards. Interaction: Reading. Justification: Introduces the main actors with RPG-style names and attributes, setting the stage for the conflict.
- Municipal Trust Gauge: Goal: Empathy/Tracking. Method: HTML/CSS progress bar. Interaction: Updates based on player choice and key events. Justification: Visually represents the central theme of 'trust'.
- Command Battle UI: Goal: Experience Conflict. Method: Dynamic HTML/CSS layout. Interaction: Automated, turn-based display of actions from a predefined script. Justification: The most direct and engaging way to fulfill the user's core requirement of highlighting the mayor vs. council showdown.
- Grid-based Info Cards (Timeline/Issues): Goal: Inform (Background). Method: Styled HTML grid. Interaction: Reading. Justification: Replaces simple lists with a more visually organized and engaging card layout, improving readability. Two new 'issue' cards were added to replace the deleted chart, deepening the political context.
-->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DotGothic16&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700&family=RocknRoll+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-main: #00000a;
            --bg-window: #0c0c34;
            --bg-card: #1a1a4a;
            --text-main: #f0f0ff;
            --text-highlight: #ffff88;
            --border-color: #ffffff;
            --hp-bar-bg: #4a5568;
            --hp-bar-fill: #48bb78;
            --trust-bar-fill: #4299e1;
            --damage-color: #f56565;
            --heal-color: #68d391;
            --font-pixel: 'DotGothic16', monospace;
            --font-sans: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
            --font-impact: 'RocknRoll One', sans-serif;
            --mayor-color: #f6ad55;
            --council-color: #63b3ed;
        }
        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-main);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
        }
        body::after {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.07) 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.07) 4px);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9999;
        }
        .pixel-font { font-family: var(--font-pixel); }
        .game-window {
            background-color: var(--bg-window);
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 0;
            padding: 1.75rem;
            box-shadow:
                inset 0 0 0 3px var(--bg-window),
                inset 0 0 0 5px var(--border-color),
                0 0 30px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.12);
        }
        .text-window {
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 1rem;
            min-height: 6rem;
        }
        .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-in-out forwards; opacity: 0; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; } }
        .damage-animation { animation: flashRed 0.5s; }
        @keyframes flashRed { 0%, 100% { background-color: transparent; } 50% { background-color: var(--damage-color); } }
        .heal-animation { animation: flashGreen 0.5s; }
        @keyframes flashGreen { 0%, 100% { background-color: transparent; } 50% { background-color: var(--heal-color); } }
        .stance-btn[aria-selected="true"] {
            outline: 3px solid var(--text-highlight);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            background-color: #2c2c64;
        }
        .progress-bar { background-color: var(--hp-bar-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
        .progress-bar-inner { transition: width 0.5s ease-in-out; }
        .screen-shake { animation: shake 0.5s cubic-bezier(.36,.07,.19,.97) both; }
        @keyframes shake {
            10%, 90% { transform: translate3d(-1px, 0, 0); }
            20%, 80% { transform: translate3d(2px, 0, 0); }
            30%, 50%, 70% { transform: translate3d(-4px, 0, 0); }
            40%, 60% { transform: translate3d(4px, 0, 0); }
        }
        .attack-icon {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            opacity: 0;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .attack-anim-council { animation: attack-right 1.5s ease-out forwards; }
        .attack-anim-mayor { animation: attack-left 1.5s ease-out forwards; }
        @keyframes attack-right {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(0.5); opacity: 1; }
            99% { transform: translate(200%, 0) scale(1.5); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: translate(200%, 0) scale(1.5); opacity: 0; }
        }
        @keyframes attack-left {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(0.5); opacity: 1; }
            99% { transform: translate(-200%, 0) scale(1.5); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: translate(-200%, 0) scale(1.5); opacity: 0; }
        }
        .ending-visual-sunset {
            width: 80px; height: 40px; background: linear-gradient(to top, #ffcc00, #ff6600, #330033);
            border-radius: 40px 40px 0 0; margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            animation: sunset 4s ease-in-out forwards;
        }
        @keyframes sunset { from { transform: translateY(0); } to { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; } }
        .ending-visual-sprout {
            font-size: 3rem;
            animation: sprout 3s ease-out forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        }
        @keyframes sprout {
            0% { transform: scale(0); opacity: 0; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }
        .dialogue-bubble {
            max-width: 85%;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .dialogue-bubble-left {
            background-color: #2c2c64;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .dialogue-bubble-right {
            background-color: #4a2c64;
            margin-left: auto;
        }
        .dialogue-avatar {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .typing-cursor {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 1em;
            background-color: var(--text-main);
            animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
        }
        @keyframes blink { 50% { opacity: 0; } }
       
        .dialogue-wrapper {
            opacity: 0;
        }
        .dialogue-wrapper.slide-in-left {
            animation: slideInLeft 0.5s ease-out forwards;
        }
        .dialogue-wrapper.slide-in-right {
            animation: slideInRight 0.5s ease-out forwards;
        }
        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }
        @keyframes slideInRight {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        .sunrise-title {
            font-family: var(--font-impact);
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, #c471ed, #f64f59, #fef08a 80%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            background-size: 100% 250%;
            background-position: 50% 100%;
            transform: translateY(100%);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: 
                sunrise-color-anim 5s 1.5s ease-out forwards,
                sunrise-rise-anim 5s 1.5s ease-out forwards;
        }
        @keyframes sunrise-color-anim {
            to { background-position: 50% 0%; }
        }
        @keyframes sunrise-rise-anim {
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1;}
        }
       
        .stagger-item {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
        }
        .stagger-item.is-visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .flow-node, .flow-arrow, .flow-path-item {
            transition: background-color 0.5s, border-color 0.5s, color 0.5s;
        }
        .flow-path-item.highlighted {
            background-color: var(--text-highlight);
            border-color: var(--text-highlight);
            color: var(--bg-window);
        }
        .push-indicator {
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease-out;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }
        .push-indicator.is-visible {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        .push-indicator.fade-out {
            opacity: 0;
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            40% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            60% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        }
        .chapter-badge {
            font-family: var(--font-pixel);
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            background-color: var(--text-highlight);
            color: var(--bg-window);
            padding: 0.1rem 0.6rem;
            display: inline-block;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        }
        .mayor-card { border-left: 3px solid var(--mayor-color); }
        .council-card { border-left: 3px solid var(--council-color); }
        #start-battle-btn {
            animation: btn-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
        }
        @keyframes btn-pulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.4); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.85), 0 0 6px rgba(255,100,100,0.5); }
        }
        button { cursor: crosshair; }
        #trust-bar {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #e53e3e 0%, #ecc94b 50%, #48bb78 100%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-2 md:p-6">

<main id="main-container" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">

    <header class="text-center game-window">
        <p class="pixel-font text-yellow-300 fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">🎭 THE・劇場型ポリティクス 🎭</p>
        <div class="h-[2.5rem] md:h-[3rem] overflow-hidden my-2">
            <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl sunrise-title">イトー市・タクボクエストⅱ</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg mt-1 fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">～欠如した説明責任とカオスの中で～</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Chapter 0: Opening -->
    <section id="opening" class="game-window" data-animation-section>
        <div class="text-center mb-1"><span class="chapter-badge">CHAPTER 0</span></div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold pixel-font mb-3 text-center">オープニング：物語の登場人物</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm" data-animation-chain="1" style="opacity: 0;">温泉と観光のまち「イトー市」。この物語は、二つの勢力の対立を中心に進む…。</p>
       
        <!-- Character Introductions -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div class="p-3 mayor-card" style="background-color: var(--bg-card);">
                <h3 class="text-lg pixel-font text-center" style="color: var(--mayor-color);">👩‍🦳 夢想の改革者 タクボ</h3>
                <p class="mt-2" data-animation-chain="2" style="opacity: 0;">「市民派」を掲げ既成勢力に挑む新市長。逆境でも公約実現に執念を燃やすが、疑惑への説明は論理的に破綻。法的権利を盾に徹底抗戦する。ＳＮＳの呪文で「秘技・論点ずらし」を連発する。</p>
                <p class="mt-2 pixel-font"><span class="text-yellow-300">スキル:</span> <span data-animation-chain="3" style="opacity: 0;">黙秘権の盾 / 論点ずらしの19.2秒 / 目くらましSNS活用術</span></p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-3 council-card" style="background-color: var(--bg-card);">
                <h3 class="text-lg pixel-font text-center" style="color: var(--council-color);">🏛️ 秩序の守護者 ギカイ</h3>
                <p class="mt-2" data-animation-chain="4" style="opacity: 0;">市政の安定と継続性を重んじる市議会の多数派。市長の倫理観を問題視し、議会の権威を守るため立ち上がる。手続きと数の力を武器とする。旧態依然とした伏魔殿（市役所）の守護者という側面も…。</p>
                <p class="mt-2 pixel-font"><span class="text-yellow-300">スキル:</span> <span data-animation-chain="5" style="opacity: 0;">百条委員会の剣 / 包囲網作戦 / 伝家の宝刀・不信任決議</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 mb-4 text-sm font-bold">この問題、あなたはどう見る？</p>
        <div id="stance-selector" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-center">
            <!-- Stance buttons will be injected here -->
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Trust Gauge -->
    <div id="trust-gauge-container" class="game-window">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm pixel-font mb-1">
            <span>市政信頼度</span>
            <span><span id="trust-value">--</span> / 100</span>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar w-full h-4">
            <div id="trust-bar" class="progress-bar-inner h-full" style="width: 50%;"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Chapter 1: Chronicle -->
    <section id="chapter1" class="game-window" data-animation-section>
        <div class="text-center mb-1"><span class="chapter-badge">CHAPTER 1</span></div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold pixel-font mb-4 text-center">第1章：疑惑と謎のラビリンス</h2>
        <div id="timeline-container" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-2 gap-y-4 text-sm">
            <!-- Timeline cards will be injected here -->
        </div>
    </section>
   
    <!-- Chapter 2: Coliseum -->
    <section id="chapter2" class="game-window" data-animation-section>
        <div class="text-center mb-1"><span class="chapter-badge">CHAPTER 2</span></div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold pixel-font mb-4 text-center">第2章：バトルの火種</h2>
        <div id="issue-grid" class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
            <!-- Issue cards will be injected here -->
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Chapter 3: Battle -->
    <section id="chapter3" class="game-window" data-animation-section>
        <div class="text-center mb-1"><span class="chapter-badge">CHAPTER 3</span></div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold pixel-font mb-3 text-center text-red-400">第3章：決戦！百条委員会</h2>
        <div id="battle-arena" class="hidden relative">
            <div id="animation-layer" class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden"></div>
            <!-- Battle UI -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-center pixel-font">
                <div id="mayor-card">
                    <p>👩‍🦳 夢想の改革者 タクボ</p>
                    <div class="progress-bar w-full h-3 mt-1"><div id="mayor-hp" class="progress-bar-inner h-full" style="width: 100%; background-color: var(--mayor-color);"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div id="council-card">
                    <p>🏛️ 秩序の守護者 ギカイ</p>
                    <div class="progress-bar w-full h-3 mt-1"><div id="council-hp" class="progress-bar-inner h-full" style="width: 100%; background-color: var(--council-color);"></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Message Window -->
            <div id="battle-message" class="text-window mt-3 text-sm pixel-font" role="status" aria-live="polite">
                <p>戦いの火蓋が切られた…</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="start-battle-wrapper" class="relative mt-16">
                 <div id="push-indicator" class="absolute -top-14 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center pointer-events-none">
                    <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-black pixel-font px-3 py-1 rounded mb-1 whitespace-nowrap">ここをプッシュ！</span>
                    <span class="text-3xl text-yellow-400">👇</span>
                </div>
            <button id="start-battle-btn" class="w-full bg-red-700 hover:bg-red-800 p-2 pixel-font text-lg">▶ BATTLE START ◀</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Chapter 4: Commentary -->
    <section id="chapter4" class="game-window" data-animation-section>
        <div class="text-center mb-1"><span class="chapter-badge">CHAPTER 4</span></div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold pixel-font mb-4 text-center">第４章：徹底解説・イヤナギが斬る！</h2>
        <div id="commentary-container">
            <!-- Profiles -->
            <div id="commentator-profiles" class="mb-4">
                 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm mb-4">
                     <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2" style="background-color: var(--bg-card);">
                         <div class="dialogue-avatar">👨‍🦲</div>
                         <div>
                            <h4 class="pixel-font text-blue-400">進行役はイトー支局 アオチャン</h4>
                            <p class="text-xs mt-1">川勝前知事の"騒動"も最前線で取材した不信任決議取材のプロ。質問の切れ味から、静新のプリゴジンの異名を取る。</p>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2" style="background-color: var(--bg-card);">
                         <div class="dialogue-avatar">👩‍🏫</div>
                         <div>
                              <h4 class="pixel-font text-green-400">ご存じ政治学者 イヤナギ先生</h4>
                              <p class="text-xs mt-1">知的な雰囲気と歯に衣着せぬ物言いでお茶の間に人気。テレビのコメンテーターにひっぱりだこの論客。</p>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                 </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Dialogue -->
            <div id="dialogue-area" class="space-y-3 mb-4">
                <!-- Dialogue will be injected here -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Chapter 5: Final Decision -->
    <section id="chapter5" class="game-window hidden" data-animation-section>
        <div class="text-center mb-1"><span class="chapter-badge">FINAL CHAPTER</span></div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold pixel-font mb-4 text-center">最終章：タクボの決断は？</h2>
        <div id="final-choice-container" class="mt-6 text-center">
           
            <div class="pixel-font p-3 mb-4 border-2 border-dashed">
                <h3 class="text-lg text-yellow-300 mb-2">今後のスケジュール</h3>
                <div class="text-sm space-y-2">
                    <div class="flow-node flow-path-item p-2 border" data-path-id="start">不信任案 可決 (2025/9/1)</div>
                    <div class="flow-arrow text-2xl">↓</div>
                    <div class="flow-node flow-path-item p-2 border" data-path-id="choice-point">市長の決断 (期限: 9/11)</div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2">
                        <div id="final-choices-flow-dissolve">
                           <div class="flow-arrow text-2xl">↓</div>
                           <div class="flow-node flow-path-item p-2 border" data-path-id="dissolve-1">議会解散</div>
                           <div class="flow-arrow text-2xl">↓</div>
                           <div class="flow-node flow-path-item p-2 border" data-path-id="dissolve-2">市議選 (期限: 10/21)</div>
                        </div>
                         <div id="final-choices-flow-resign">
                           <div class="flow-arrow text-2xl">↓</div>
                           <div class="flow-node flow-path-item p-2 border" data-path-id="resign-1">自ら辞職</div>
                           <div class="flow-arrow text-2xl">↓</div>
                           <div class="flow-node flow-path-item p-2 border" data-path-id="resign-2">市長選 (期限: 10/31)</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="choice-prompt-wrapper">
                <p class="pixel-font text-yellow-300 text-lg mb-3">運命の選択</p>
                <p class="mb-4">あなたが市長なら、どちらの扉を開く？</p>
                <div id="final-choices" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="ending-screen" class="hidden text-center p-4 mt-4"></div>
    </section>


    <footer class="text-center text-xs text-gray-500 pixel-font mt-6">
        <p>出典：ウェブ上の公開情報</p>
        <p class="mt-1">お断り：本コンテンツはAIが制作した架空のストーリーで、特定のゲームや実在の人物とは一切関係ありません</p>
    </footer>

</main>

<script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    // --- DATA ---
    const DATA = {
        stances: [
            { id: 'pro-mayor', label: '市長を信じる', trust: 75 },
            { id: 'pro-council', label: '議会を支持する', trust: 25 },
            { id: 'neutral', label: 'まずは様子を見る', trust: 50 },
        ],
        timeline: [
            { event: "疑惑の発端", detail: "「市長の学歴は嘘」との匿名文書が全議員に届く。", icon: "✉️" },
            { event: "謎の「チラ見せ」", detail: "市長が卒業証書らしきものを見せるが、確認させず不信感を招く。", icon: "📜" },
            { event: "19.2秒の証言", detail: "百条委員会で『19.2秒見せた』と証言。これが偽証罪疑惑の引き金に。", icon: "⏱️" },
            { event: "あの人がサプライズ登場", detail: "メガソーラー問題の背後から『ウィッグの盟主 ナンバ』が突如参戦！物語は新展開へ。", icon: "👨‍🦳" },
            { event: "不信任案、可決！", detail: "9月議会で不信任案が全会一致で可決。市長は刑事告発され、議会解散で反撃。市民を巻き込んだ選挙戦へ！", icon: "💥" }
        ],
        issues: [
